Title: Last Stand (2)
Plot: Dr. Jackson's undercover mission to a Goa'uld summit is complicated by the arrival of a surprise guest. The rest of the team face a full-scale invasion of the Tok'ra homeworld.
GuestStars: Anna-Louise Plowman, Natasha Khade, Kevin Durand, William de Vry, Jennifer Calvert, Courtenay J. Stevens, Anthony Ulc, Kwesi Ameyaw, Sue Mathew, Bonnie Kilroe, Paul Anthony
